- Straight.

06:13.712 --> 06:14.711
- Rivers?
- Straight.

06:14.713 --> 06:15.711
Mountains?

06:15.713 --> 06:16.779
Straight.

06:16.781 --> 06:18.214
Straight,
straight, straight.

06:18.216 --> 06:19.682
Did you bring
what we discussed?

06:20.785 --> 06:22.084
Wow! Yeah, I did.

06:22.086 --> 06:23.586
So, this is 390 miles,

06:23.588 --> 06:27.123
the line I did from
Los Angeles to San Francisco.

06:27.125 --> 06:28.658
I ran 16 crews for 6 months.

06:28.660 --> 06:30.960
