01:16:57.839 --> 01:17:00.874
<i>Uh, ballpark,
I think our regenerators have</i>

01:17:00.876 --> 01:17:03.443
<i>around a 10% or 15% tolerance.</i>

01:17:03.445 --> 01:17:05.846
